c: 7
v: 164
t: "Era jjukira e kibiina mu bo bwe kyagamba nti, lwaki mubuulirira e kibiina kya bantu nga Katonda ajja kubazikiriza, oba ajja kubabonereza n’ebibonerezo e bisuffu, bo nebagamba nti tukikola lwa kweggyako musango ewa Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe, ate sinakindi nabo bayinza okutya Katonda"